<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Identitet, mediji i mentalno zdravlje</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
  *,*::before,*::after { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

  :root {
    --bg:       #111111;
    --text:     #e8e8e8;
    --muted:    #9a9a9a;
    --dim:      #666;
    --accent:   #d4a054;
    --border:   rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    --radius:   10px;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text);
    background: var(--bg);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 16.5px;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════════
     HERO SECTION
  ══════════════════════════════════ */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 430px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: 
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 85% 55%, rgba(180, 120, 50, 0.4) 0%, transparent 55%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 60% at 75% 70%, rgba(140, 80, 30, 0.25) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 50% at 60% 0%, rgba(60, 40, 20, 0.3) 0%, transparent 70%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1410 0%, #111 100%);
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 50%, transparent 20%, rgba(17,17,17,0.85) 65%);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 900px;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 40px;
  }

  .hero-text {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 3;
    max-width: 520px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: rise 0.9s ease forwards;
  }

  .hero-text h1 {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5.5vw, 54px);
    font-weight: 420;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .hero-text .subtitle {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hero-mic {
    position: absolute;
    right: 0;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    z-index: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: micFloat 0.9s 0.2s ease forwards;
  }

  .hero-mic img {
    height: 90%;
    width: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
    object-position: right;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 20px 80px rgba(180, 120, 40, 0.4)) drop-shadow(0 4px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.6));
  }

  @keyframes micFloat {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════════
     CONTENT AREA
  ══════════════════════════════════ */
  .page {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 28px 120px;
  }

  /* ── PROSE ── */
  .prose {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: rise 0.8s 0.45s ease forwards;
  }

  .prose p {
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 22px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .prose p strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ── FULL-WIDTH DIVIDER ── */
  .full-divider {
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  /* ── QUOTE SECTION (between hero and content) ── */
  .quote-section {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 28px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: rise 0.8s 0.3s ease forwards;
  }

  .quote {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .quote-img {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .quote-body blockquote {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .quote-body cite {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--dim);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* ── CONTENT DIVIDER (700px) ── */
  .content-divider {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  /* ── FEATURED ── */
  .featured {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: rise 0.8s 0.5s ease forwards;
  }

  .featured h2 {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .featured-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .featured-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--muted);
    padding: 14px 18px;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: background 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .featured-list li:hover {
    background: #222;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .featured-list li::before {
    content: '';
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ── VIDEOS ── */
  .videos-section {
    margin-top: 56px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: rise 0.8s 0.6s ease forwards;
  }

  .videos-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .video-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .video-card {
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .video-card.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .video-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  }

  .video-card iframe {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16/9;
    display: block;
    border: none;
  }

  .video-card .video-label {
    padding: 10px 14px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--dim);
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    margin-top: 72px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--dim);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: rise 0.8s 0.7s ease forwards;
  }

  /* ── ANIMATION ── */
  @keyframes rise {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero { min-height: 480px; }
    .hero-inner { padding: 48px 24px; }
    .hero-text { max-width: 100%; }
    .hero-mic { right: 0; }
    .hero-mic img { height: 70%; }
    .quote-section { padding: 30px 20px; }
    .quote { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; gap: 16px; }
    .quote-img { width: 68px; height: 68px; }
    .page { padding: 48px 20px 80px; }
    .video-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- ══ HERO ══ -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1>Identitet, mediji<br>i mentalno zdravlje</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Projekt učenika 2.F razreda</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-mic">
      <img src="mikrofon.png" alt="Mikrofon">
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══ DIVIDER (full width) ══ -->
<div class="full-divider"></div>

<!-- ══ QUOTE ══ -->
<div class="quote-section">
  <div class="quote">
    <img class="quote-img" src="media.jpg" alt="Mediji i identitet">
    <div class="quote-body">
      <blockquote>„We shape our tools, and thereafter our tools shape us."</blockquote>
      <cite>— Marshall McLuhan</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══ DIVIDER (700px) ══ -->
<div class="content-divider"></div>

<!-- ══ CONTENT ══ -->
<div class="page">

  <div class="prose">
    <p>
      U svijetu u kojem notifikacije oblikuju našu svakodnevicu, a glazba nas prati od jutra do večeri, 
      pitanje identiteta više nije jednostavno. Tko smo kada smo online, a tko kada se ekran ugasi? 
      Koliko na naše misli, osjećaje i odluke utječu mediji koje svakodnevno konzumiramo — i jesmo li toga uopće svjesni?
    </p>
    <p>
      Projekt <i>Podcasti - identitet, mediji i mentalno zdravlje</i> nastao je iz potrebe da se ta pitanja istraže dublje i iskrenije. 
      Učenici 2.F razreda, uz mentorstvo prof. Marije Cestarić, kroz multimedijske radove uranjaju u svijet 
      digitalne stvarnosti koja nas okružuje, ali i oblikuje. Kroz vlastita istraživanja i kreativne pristupe 
      otvaraju teme poput utjecaja glazbe na naš mozak i emocije, odnosa između online i stvarnog identiteta, 
      uloge influencera u razgovorima o mentalnom zdravlju te izazova digitalnog preopterećenja.
    </p>
    <p>
      Ovaj projekt nije samo niz zadataka — on je prostor za propitivanje, eksperimentiranje i izražavanje. 
      Korištenjem suvremenih digitalnih alata učenici razvijaju ne samo tehničke vještine, već i sposobnost 
      kritičkog promišljanja, komunikacije i timskog rada. Rezultat su radovi koji ne nude jednostavne odgovore, 
      već potiču na razmišljanje: o nama samima, o svijetu u kojem živimo i o tome kako pronaći ravnotežu između njih.
    </p>
  </div>


  <div class="videos-section">
    <h2>Pogledaj radove</h2>

    <div class="video-grid">
      <div class="video-card">
        <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/73SbVarMiDY" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        <div class="video-label">Pink Mics – Lucija Krajnik i Zara Zrnić</div>
      </div>
      <div class="video-card">
        <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Mc-sx25mCkw" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        <div class="video-label">Moderni problemi – Vita Hudika, Maša Gračan i Lucija Vrljić</div>
      </div>
      <div class="video-card">
        <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RBlLKfVvmgY" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        <div class="video-label">Influenceri i mentalno zdravlje – Frida Ladan, Mia Stanić i Iva Janjuš</div>
      </div>
      <div class="video-card">
        <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/t2o-EMPIQoQ" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        <div class="video-label">Na loptama – Dorian Kovačević, Niko Marić i Nikola Fiolić</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2.F razred · prof. Marija Cestarić · 2026.
  </footer>

</div>

<script>
const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.video-card');
const observer = new IntersectionObserver(entries => {
  entries.forEach((entry, i) => {
    if (entry.isIntersecting) {
      setTimeout(() => entry.target.classList.add('visible'), i * 120);
      observer.unobserve(entry.target);
    }
  });
}, { threshold: 0.15 });
cards.forEach(c => observer.observe(c));
</script>

</body>
</html>
